# Minecraft Version(s): 26.1.x
## Changes:
- Lang Files are now getting automatically synced with crowdin with new releases
- Increased probability of getting Enchanted Books in loot of Rise structure
- Projectiles shot by a Crossbow with Flare enchantment now also explode after 1-5 seconds (increases with level (lvl 1 = 1 sec)) when no entity/block was hit before
- Projectiles shot by a Crossbow with Flare enchantment now get removed when they explode
- Added Velocity enchantment (doubles speed of shot projectiles. Can be obtained in enchanting tables and on random loot)
- Added Incognito enchantment (hides the wearers name tag. Can be obtained by trading books and on random loot)
- Added Bounce enchantment (lets the wearer bounce all over the place. Can be obtained in enchanting tables and on random loot)
- Removed trigger for chat messages from the ingame wiki with links to our new wiki (Entries on the wiki will be created by me over time)
- Removed Poppy Peace and Sting enchantments due to changes of how Entity Anger works

## Fixes:
- Fixed a typo in Pufferfish enchantment description